    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-02-05T04:30:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-02-05T04:30:00-05:00" n="58"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d58">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">756D.94/117: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul General at Batavia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foote</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Batavia</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-02-05T17:00:00+07:30"
                            >February 5, 1941—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received February 5—7:49 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Referring to the reports that the Japanese Vice Minister for Foreign Affairs
                    had rejected the Netherlands statement concerning the incorporation of the
                    Netherlands Indies into the new order ii East Asia, Yoshizawa, the head of the
                    Japanese delegation in Batavia has just issued the following statement: <pb
                        facs="0067" n="57" xml:id="pg_57"/>
                    <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“With regard to the report carried by Domei on the third instant
                            concerning Vice Minister Ohashi I have just received an official
                            telegram contradicting the information contained in such report.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>Repeated to Tokyo.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Foote</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
